---
title: Hearty Chicken Stew with potatoes and pesto
description: This chicken and carrot stew has a bright and herby flavour profile, meaning it's hearty but suitable for the summer too. Along with the main ingredients you also have potatoes and pesto, which make for a more filling and flavourful meal.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R11_W40_IE_IEXQC0027-3_Main_high-df7a65f3.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.ie/recipecards/card/64b4f7dc66be97d461e92974.pdf
servings: 2
source: https://www.hellofresh.ie/recipes/hearty-chicken-stew-64b4f7dc66be97d461e92974
cuisine: European
author: HelloFresh
time required: 25 minutes
nutrition:
  calories: 633 kcal
  fat: 27.1 g
